# Documentation Principles

## Only explain concepts and APIs that are unique to Confect

Don't explain concepts or APIs that are specific to Effect or Convex—link to the appropriate page(s) in their respective documentation instead. The Confect documentation should focus only on the features which are unique to Confect, and how those features interface with Effect and Convex APIs.
